Your Queries, Simplified

Questions? Answers!

Find quick answers to the most common questions about our platform

What is Gerbo?

Gerbo is a 24/7 AI receptionist that answers your calls, captures caller info, and sends you a summary by email or SMS (coming soon).

Can I keep my current phone number?

Yes — Gerbo forwards calls and works with your existing line.

Will clients know it’s AI?

Not unless you tell them — Gerbo uses a polite, human-sounding African voice. If you'd like you can add an AI disclaimer during the greeting message.

How do I get started?

Check out our demo, get in contact, and we'll get Gerbo to work.

Is Gerbo GDPR-compliant and secure?

Yes — all data captured by Gerbo is encrypted and stored according to GDPR standards.

Can Gerbo take bookings or just messages?

Gerbo answers simple business related questions and captures caller details so you can follow up in your own time. Booking system integration coming soon.

How many calls can Gerbo handle?

Dependable at any volume — each plan includes call limits, and you can add more anytime.

Is there a free trial available?

Not yet — but you can hear Gerbo in action with our interactive demo!

Can I customise Gerbo’s greeting?

Yes, you can personalise what Gerbo says.

Feel free to mail us for any enquiries : support@gerbospeaks.com
